- "Married-civ-spouse" refers to individuals who are married and living with their spouse;
- "Bachelors" refers to individuals who have completed a bachelor's degree;
- "20%" tax bracket indicates the tax rate applicable to the individual's income;
- "Employment label" refers to additional classification or tags assigned to an individual's employment record.

